Objects.Name: dress pink taffeta
Objects.Description: A pretty pink taffeta dress lies crumpled on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's a beautifuly tailored pink dress.  You would look quite nice in it.

Objects.Name: dress blue silk
Objects.Description: A pretty blue silk dress is getting wrinkled and dirty lying on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's a beautifully tailored silk dress.  You would look smashing in it.

Objects.Name: dress white cotton
Objects.ShortDescription: a pretty pristine white cotton dress
Objects.Description: A pretty white cotton dress has been tossed to the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's a lovely cotton dress.  You would look quite the woman in it.

Objects.Name: dress beige burlap
Objects.Description: An ugly beige burlap dress looks very like a sack of potatoes on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: Eyugh.  Gross.  You don't actually want to wear _this_, do you?

Objects.Name: dress swirling beautiful multi-colored
Objects.Description: A beautiful, swirling, multi-colored dress is getting soiled on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: The dress is made from many different colors, and just seems to flow morethan rest.  You would look more beautiful than you ever have in this lusciousgarb.

Objects.Name: talisman demon-faced demon faced charming
Objects.Description: A talisman with the face of a demon on it has been thrown to the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It has a picture of a disgustingly ugly daemon on it.  It looks quite evil,but it also looks very powerful.  You can feel the magic flowing from it to yourhand.  You're torn on whether to use it or not.

Objects.Name: robe leisure
Objects.Description: A robe of leisure is on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: Oh, my, you could just sink right into this robe.  It looks so very*comfortable.  *

Objects.Name: rattle tar
Objects.Description: A tar rattle just insists on your getting it.
Objects.ExtraDescription: Awww...  Look at it!  You just wnat to pick it right up and rattle it.

Objects.Name: scroll fear
Objects.Description: A scroll with the description of a man screaming at the top of his lungs has been left here.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It looks pretty frightening.

Objects.Name: crown spikes
Objects.Description: A crown with very sharp spikes has been very carelessly left here to rust.
Objects.ExtraFlags: NoInvis, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: The hat itself is rather disconcerting.  Huge, very sharp, razorlike spikesprotrude from the top; it's pa268ed with cloth at the bottom, so it looks likeit might be worth with relative comfort--but it sure looks sinister.

Objects.Name: robe fear
Objects.Description: A black, bloodstained robe is crumpled on the floor.
Objects.ExtraKeyword: robe fear black blood stained bloodstained
Objects.ExtraDescription: This strange robe seems to absorb the light around it.  It's stained with theblood of many men.

Objects.Name: ball chain
Objects.Description: A ball and chain lies on the ground.
Objects.ExtraFlags: NoRent, Invisible, Magic, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Thief
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's a huge steel bowling ball--looks to way several hundred kilograms--witha long chain extended to one legiron...

Objects.Name: manacles handcuffs
Objects.Description: Some manacles are on the ground.
Objects.ExtraFlags: NoRent, Invisible, Magic, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Thief

Objects.Name: key cell cellkey
Objects.Description: A cellkey has been hung on the wall.

Objects.Name: knife butcher
Objects.Description: A huge butcher knife has been left on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It looks quite effective as a knife.  It's very sharp and has just the rightamount of blood from previous kills.

Objects.Name: armbands pitch black
Objects.ShortDescription: a pair of pitch black armbands
Objects.Description: A pair of pitch black armbands has been thrown to the ground.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: These armbands are made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are.  They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: leggings pitch black
Objects.ShortDescription: a pair of pitch black leggings
Objects.Description: A pair of pitch black leggings lie on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: The leggings are made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are. They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: boots pitch black
Objects.ShortDescription: a pair of pitch black boots
Objects.Description: A pair of pitch black boots lie on the ground.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: The boots are made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are. They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: gloves pitch black
Objects.ShortDescription: a pair of pitch black gloves
Objects.Description: A pair of pitch black gloves are on the ground.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: The gloves are made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are. They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: blade terror
Objects.Description: The Blade of Terror has been thrown to the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: The blade is made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are. They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: armor pitch black plate
Objects.Description: A pitch black plate armor has been carelessly left behind.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: The armor is made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are. They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: headdress terror
Objects.Description: The Headdress of Terror has been dropped here.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: This hea268ress is made from the same metal as the Temple of Terror is madefrom.  Perhaps they came from the same blacksmith.

Objects.Name: ring pitch black
Objects.Description: A ring of pitch-black metal is half-sticking out of the floor.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: The ring is made from the same kind of stone the outer area of theHigh Path in Vice Island are. They are probably imported from the same place.

Objects.Name: cloak darkness
Objects.ShortDescription: a cloak of the purest black
Objects.Description: A cloak of darkness is in a heap on the ground.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, Magic, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Cleric, Warrior
Objects.ExtraDescription: The material the cloak is made from just seems to suck the light right in.You can still see around you, but things just look dimmer.  It's rally o268.

Objects.Name: armor scale iridescent
Objects.Description: An armor made out of the irridescent scales of a dragon is on the floor.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, NoDonate, NoInvis, Invisible, AntiGood, AntiNeutral, Warrior

Objects.Name: whip cat o' nine tails
Objects.Description: A cat o' nine tails is on the ground here.
Objects.ExtraFlags: Humming, NoDonate, Magic, NoDrop, Bless, AntiGood, AntiEvil, Cleric

Objects.Name: spectacles rimmed 4-eyes four-eyes four eyes
Objects.Description: A pair of wire-rimmed spectacles is about to get crushed if it is left on the ground.

Objects.Name: key strangely shaped
Objects.Description: A strangely shaped key is lying on the ground.

Objects.Name: key black pitch
Objects.Description: A pitch-black key is lying on the ground.

Objects.Name: key glass
Objects.Description: A transparent glass key lies on the ground.

Objects.Name: key stone
Objects.Description: A stone key lies on the ground.

Objects.Name: key redwood
Objects.Description: A redwood key lies on the ground.

Objects.Name: key iron dull
Objects.Description: A dull iron key lies on the ground. *yawn*

Objects.Name: key tiny
Objects.Description: You almost miss a tiny key on the ground.

Objects.Name: key burning
Objects.Description: A red-hot key glows brightly on the ground.

Objects.Name: potion red glowing
Objects.Description: A glowing red potion bubbles in a canister on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It looks rather strange.  Somehow you get the feeling it might not be a goodidea to quaff this one.

Objects.Name: potion blue shining
Objects.Description: A shining blue potion is in a canister on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It looks informative.

Objects.Name: potion green
Objects.Description: A green potion is in a canister on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It has a sign on it that reads, "drink me.  "

Objects.Name: purple potion
Objects.ShortDescription: a purple potion of giant strength
Objects.Description: A purple potion of giant strength.
Objects.ExtraDescription: A thin label says, "use this to wield heavy weapons.  "

Objects.Name: cloak wisdom
Objects.Description: A green cloak of wisdom is in a heap on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's of a silvery metal, and practically eminates magic.

Objects.Name: cloak forgetfulness
Objects.Description: A hazel cloak of forgetfulness is in a big heap on the ground.
Objects.ExtraDescription: It's of a strange hazel material, and doesn't look particularly helpful.
